Package: vnalpha
Version: 0.1.0
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-pip
Recommends: curl
Maintainer: OpenStock Maintainers <maintainers@openstock.local>
Description: VnAlpha — Alpha discovery research CLI/TUI for Vietnamese equities
 A host-native research tool providing a command-line interface and
 interactive TUI for browsing Vietnamese equity research candidates.
 .
 This package installs a vendored Python virtual environment under
 /opt/vnalpha/venv so it does not interfere with system Python packages.
 .
 IMPORTANT: This package is for research observation only.
 It does not expose brokerage, order, account, portfolio, or trading
 functionality. The installed binary connects only to the local
 vnstock-service data platform at 127.0.0.1:6900.
 .
 User data (DuckDB warehouse) lives under /var/lib/openstock/warehouse
 and is NEVER removed on package upgrade or removal.
Installed-Size: 1
Homepage: https://github.com/openstock/openstock
